### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@branchId = branch-uuid-here
@donorId = user-uuid-here
@donationId = donation-uuid-here

### Create a new donation
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.0,
  "currency": "USD",
  "method": "Cash",
  "isAnonymous": false,
  "message": "Monthly tithe",
  "branchId": "{{branchId}}",
  "donorId": "{{donorId}}"
}

### List donations of a church
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/donations

### List donations of a branch
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/donations

### Get donation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/donations/{{donationId}}
